thread.title: Dinise Dobbey

author: Dinise Dobbey
title: Dinise Dobbey
text: I was thrilled that they had the part in stock. I paid for priority shipping and expected to receive it in 2 days and scheduled the repair for the following day. It came in 5 days...the same day I was leaving town. Now I have to wait until I return and reschedule the repair. It was an inconvenience to myself as well as the mechanic. Very disappointed.
